<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT79">
<l>āyntukoṇ ṭātip perumāṉai yaṉpiṉāl</l>
<l>vāynta maṉattirutta vallārka ḷēyntata</l>
<l>meykunta māka virumpuvarē tāmumtam</l>
<l>vaikuntaṅ kāṇpār viraintu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who, thinking out of love of the Primordial Lord,</l>
<l>are able to place [Him] in [their] excellent hearts,</l>
<l>Will desire their bodies fitted [with souls] to give [them] distress,</l>
<l>wishing to see their Vaikuṇṭha swiftly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
